  <body>
    <metal:macro define-macro="bell"
                 tal:define="url content/absolute_url|nothing;
                             title content/Title|nothing;">

          <div class="alert alert-danger">
            <span class="oi oi-bell float-left d-none d-sm-inline" aria-hidden="true" title="Important announcement follows"></span>
            <h4><a href="">Response to the loss of George Floyd</a></h4>
            <p>
              Dr. Whitehurst, Vice Provost for Educational Equity addresses
              the loss of George Floyd in Minnesota, Breonna Taylor in
              Kentucky, and Ahmaud Arbrey in Georgia as victims of
              unconscionable acts of violence.
            </p>
          </div>


